name: Lavinia Model
description:
This download is offered as part of a graphic design thesis project at ArtCenter College of Design. The project is called IDIOT and is a study on contemporary privacy and camouflage.

(If you download the model, I would really appreciate it if you could send me a jpg or any file of the work you do with this model to laviniala(at)live.com. I would like to put it in my thesis book. Please include your name so I can credit you)
